creator: Bound Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Ride Electric Scooters? Share The Fun with Friends!

Why not try Bound scooters and e-bikes for enjoyment, access a new way to get around. With Bound, you can easily share the delight of riding with friends. With our environmentally friendly vehicles, not only traveling through the wonders of the city, you are also making an impact in the world by reducing co2 emissions, transport congestion, and noise pollution! Look no further, Bound is the perfect app for enjoying city exploration on electric scooters and bikes!

1. Download the Bound app
2. Find the nearest e-scooters or e-bikes
3. Create an account.
4. Add credit to wallet
5. Scan QR code
6. Unlock vehicle
7. Ride

Stay safe by wearing a helmet and obeying traffic laws while sharing the road with others.
Remember, park vehicle properly to prevent accidents; make your city happy.
